WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.640 --> 00:00:02.040
Hey, good morning, family.

00:00:00.640 --> 00:00:01.690
Praise the Lord.

00:00:00.640 --> 00:00:02.816
Thank you for joining us today.

00:00:02.816 --> 00:00:06.080
Well, I have Diana with me.

00:00:06.080 --> 00:00:07.664
She's going to read a prophetic word that is in due season.

00:00:07.664 --> 00:00:14.000
I'm telling you folks, I've never seen it like this before.

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:23.360
It's like what the Lord told us, that there would be an acceleration of things: political, war, earthquakes in diverse places.

00:00:25.440 --> 00:00:29.600
The heavens—we haven't seen that yet, all the major asteroids.

00:00:44.153 --> 00:00:44.669
I had a dream of another major thing coming with an asteroid two nights ago, and with finances.

00:00:55.760 --> 00:00:59.960
And so, we see the five shakings that He said were coming.

00:00:55.760 --> 00:01:07.920
Now we're seeing this major escalation of what I told you all in prayer, I think it was like four videos ago, three videos ago, when He said, 'Pray over a megaton bomb coming into Tel Aviv.

00:01:07.920 --> 00:01:10.370
' And I had Diana Braden Google.

00:01:07.920 --> 00:01:13.760
Iran doesn't even have one of those—this massive thing that I saw.

00:01:31.360 --> 00:01:42.210
Well, I thought, 'Well, Lord, I know I hear You, and I know what You told me to watch out for, and You told me to bring it to the people.

00:01:31.360 --> 00:01:31.928
' And so I did.

00:01:31.928 --> 00:01:44.720
Then we see Trump leave the G7 summit early, like in the middle of it, and leave and go back, and he has a major meeting tonight as we're speaking.

00:01:58.058 --> 00:01:58.771
And we see China say, 'We're going to back Iran.

00:01:58.771 --> 00:02:09.440
' And I thought, 'Well, there's where the megaton bomb comes from, if China says, "Hey, we'll give you supplies or whatever you're going to need.

00:02:09.440 --> 00:02:18.330
"' If you go back to what the Lord showed me in the World War II video, I saw troops coming against Israel with red hats on.

00:02:31.368 --> 00:02:31.984
But I also saw in that what people would call the great betrayal during the Ezekiel 38 and 39 war.

00:02:31.984 --> 00:02:38.160
I told everybody, 'They will call this the great betrayal,' because I saw America standing by.

00:02:38.160 --> 00:02:43.120
Now, are we in that timeframe?

00:02:43.120 --> 00:02:47.783
No, I do not believe we're in Ezekiel 38 and 39 as of yet.

00:02:48.560 --> 00:02:49.960
I believe it's coming.

00:02:48.560 --> 00:02:53.040
I believe the hook in the jaw is coming.

00:03:06.640 --> 00:03:08.740
I believe there are escalations now.

00:03:20.800 --> 00:03:25.000
I was hearing this prophetic word that you're about to read, Diana.

00:03:20.800 --> 00:03:34.720
Maurice Sklar says he believes we're entering—we entered into Psalm 83, which, sorry to say, I'm ignorant about, but I didn't even know there was a Psalm 83 because I haven't heard anybody teach about it until I saw this prophetic word.

00:03:37.520 --> 00:03:41.852
And I was like, 'Well, hold on a minute, I haven't heard the Bible theologians talk about Psalm 83 a lot in the end times.

00:03:41.852 --> 00:03:42.640
' But I respect Maurice.

00:03:42.640 --> 00:03:46.780
I know he's a man of God, and he hears God.

00:03:49.636 --> 00:03:53.324
He has very accurate words, so it's very interesting, some of this that you're about to hear.

00:03:53.324 --> 00:03:59.840
I've talked about this in the past, but as the days go by, look, folks, words are coming to pass.

00:03:59.840 --> 00:04:02.990
And I know it's not always people's hot topic.

00:03:59.840 --> 00:04:13.920
They don't want to talk—they want to talk about the end times, the rapture, all the great, beautiful things of the revival, but we have to talk about the dark side of the coin, too.

00:04:13.920 --> 00:04:15.467
I told you, I don't just always talk about the sugar.

00:04:15.467 --> 00:04:21.200
I believe the revival is awesome, and I'm excited, but this is my main vein of warning, warning, warning.

00:04:21.200 --> 00:04:23.536
If you haven't noticed, the Lord said, 'You're called to say the hard things.

00:04:23.536 --> 00:04:26.992
' And I do it.

00:04:36.080 --> 00:04:37.716
And you know what, I want to say this: yesterday, when I apologized if I came across cranky, that was because I was corrected by the Holy Spirit.

00:04:44.136 --> 00:04:44.832
It wasn't about y'all; it was about what He said.

00:04:44.832 --> 00:04:50.400
He said, 'Brandon, come across softer toward the people.

00:04:54.267 --> 00:04:58.920
I want you to deliver it so that the ones that need to truly hear it will not click out of the video.

00:04:58.920 --> 00:05:03.600
Present it in a way that is a little bit more...

00:05:03.600 --> 00:05:09.920
' I don't even know what to say, how to say it, but I know what He's saying.

00:05:09.920 --> 00:05:14.528
So that's what I had for you yesterday.

00:05:19.360 --> 00:05:23.680
But I want to let you all know we love you, we're thankful for every single one of you, and we're so grateful that you would come and listen to us.

00:05:23.680 --> 00:05:28.000
But I'm telling you, we have a word that is in due season.

00:05:28.000 --> 00:05:39.540
I'm warning you all of a major shaking still going to happen in the Middle East with Israel, with these signs.

00:05:53.600 --> 00:06:08.300
But what I'm more concerned about is not even Israel, but about America and what has crossed the border over the last four years—past, going on four and a half years before Trump put a stop to it—what came across our border.

00:05:56.880 --> 00:06:01.780
And many people say, 'Well, Brandon, hopefully we've got these guys; they're hiding out.

00:05:56.880 --> 00:06:07.520
' And I saw funneling of hundreds of millions of dollars over the last four years for buying supplies and doing all this.

00:06:10.160 --> 00:06:13.680
We pray protection over our nation.

00:06:13.680 --> 00:06:20.480
I believe it's a time like never before that we rise up and take our dominion and authority.

00:06:25.840 --> 00:06:31.440
You know, it's like we take dominion and authority over Oklahoma; we're praying over our area.

00:06:25.840 --> 00:06:36.000
If you live in Oklahoma, you're joining in with us, but you need to do that in your hometown.

00:06:36.000 --> 00:06:49.410
One of the things that I forgot to say out of that prophetic word, when I told you I was driving around a couple of days ago, the Lord said, 'Watch small cities, unexpected locations.

00:06:49.410 --> 00:06:55.920
Like Omaha, Nebraska was one of the major cities.

00:06:55.920 --> 00:06:57.920
' He said, 'Watch Oklahoma City, watch Little Rock.

00:06:57.920 --> 00:07:09.360
' These little cities that are not too big like a New York or a Los Angeles or something like that, but there might be a couple million people in them, but it's not like, 'Oh my goodness,' you know?

00:07:11.760 --> 00:07:15.260
And the Lord told me, He said, 'Watch these places.

00:07:30.320 --> 00:07:31.720
It's Pearl Harbor events.

00:07:30.320 --> 00:07:37.940
' He said, 'Watch for that.

00:07:37.940 --> 00:07:49.680
' Remember when I told you all I heard China say, 'We must create a Pearl Harbor event,' and I saw them talking to North Korea?

00:07:49.680 --> 00:07:57.952
And North Korea was a social pariah; that's why they asked him to do it, because Kim Jong-un is not respected anywhere.

00:08:02.880 --> 00:08:04.980
I mean, he is Kim Jong-un.

00:08:09.000 --> 00:08:09.680
And I saw China becoming desperate with their finances, remember?

00:08:11.040 --> 00:08:25.304
And because they were desperate with their finances, they were like backed into a corner, and they were like the samurais that would die on their sword because it was an honor thing.

00:08:32.907 --> 00:08:35.280
And that's what the Lord said: 'You don't understand their culture versus a Western culture; they think totally different.

00:08:35.280 --> 00:08:42.280
' And the Lord told me about all this stuff, and being just an old country boy, I don't know that kind of stuff, you know?

00:08:45.080 --> 00:08:49.280
And I told Diana, I said, 'You know, the Holy Spirit's been talking to me about this.

00:08:49.280 --> 00:08:56.080
' We go over things that the Lord says because Diana's real educated.

00:08:56.080 --> 00:08:58.560
And I said, 'You know, it makes sense, doesn't it?

00:08:58.560 --> 00:09:05.590
' The way the Lord's talking to me about this, about how China thinks differently than Western culture.

00:09:25.840 --> 00:09:36.340
And I thought, you know, we see Iran now—not become what I have seen so far, but it's headed there with being set back economically, with their military, with everything.

00:09:25.840 --> 00:09:27.590
I've seen a major setback.

00:09:25.840 --> 00:09:29.040
Now, I even described the missile.

00:09:29.040 --> 00:09:32.240
This is what's so amazing, folks.

00:09:43.120 --> 00:09:55.720
I give all the glory to God, but I think it's amazing the way He comes out with the plan to tell you back in January about even the missile that I saw that Israel needed.

00:09:46.256 --> 00:09:47.600
And I saw USA on the side of this missile, and it was black and white, and it was a bunker buster.

00:09:47.600 --> 00:10:00.320
And I didn't know that Israel didn't have these missiles that were capable of going into that mountain that was a city that had nuclear stuff going on with biological weapons inside of this mountain.

00:10:00.320 --> 00:10:19.600
Whenever I was watching the news, and they showed the mountain range and where it was, and they said, 'This is where they have to hit, but they don't have the equipment without the United States' help,' I went, 'Oh my, Braden, we were...

00:10:19.600 --> 00:10:21.660
' and I go, 'Diana, did you—oh, rewind, rewind!

00:10:21.660 --> 00:10:27.840
' And I said, 'Look, they're talking about the missile that I saw.

00:10:27.840 --> 00:10:51.440
' And I told you all it's black and white and it looks like an arrowhead, and I said, 'This is the missile that they have to get from America, that they will get from America, to go inside that mountain.

00:10:51.440 --> 00:11:04.416
' But I saw 50-gallon drums coming out of that mountain to go to Damascus to try to gas the Israelis in the days ahead, and I saw trucks full of this biological weapon.

00:11:05.120 --> 00:11:10.720
And the Lord said, 'You must pray on behalf of this, because they will try to use biological weapons in the days ahead on Israel.

00:11:10.720 --> 00:11:16.960
' And it was like a mustard-looking, yellow-looking gas when they were spraying it on the people.

00:11:32.720 --> 00:11:35.870
They tried to do like crop dusters and stuff.

00:11:42.000 --> 00:11:47.950
It was like—I don't know, you know, like they were trying to get them with the spray.

00:11:49.680 --> 00:11:55.728
And I saw the people; it was a gas, and they got boils all over their skin, and it was melting their skin, and they were just dying instantly.

00:12:04.640 --> 00:12:05.690
It was awful.

00:12:04.640 --> 00:12:06.784
It was a very, very traumatic death.

00:12:06.784 --> 00:12:12.400
But when they did this, I saw Damascus with a suitcase-looking bomb thing, and it was thin.

00:12:12.400 --> 00:12:18.000
I remember looking in the spirit and the Lord showing me this.

00:12:18.928 --> 00:12:25.424
And it's even on videos, I've told you all.

00:12:25.424 --> 00:12:30.800
I have archives of prayer things that I've done with y'all, of everything I've shared.

00:12:34.764 --> 00:12:37.520
I'm very transparent, and you know, it's amazing because the Lord said, 'Damascus and Assyria will become a ruinous heap' in the Word.

00:12:43.872 --> 00:12:44.368
Well, I believe we're about to see that.

00:12:47.840 --> 00:12:50.340
I believe we could be days, weeks, whatever away from seeing Damascus become what the Bible said it would become.

00:12:50.340 --> 00:12:53.840
Then I saw Turkey, furious that this happened, and trying to come against Israel.

00:13:04.756 --> 00:13:05.193
It became a really nasty mess.

00:13:05.193 --> 00:13:08.684
Well, where was America during this timeframe?

00:13:14.880 --> 00:13:15.333
I remember I told you, I want you to think about—go back, because Braden and I put these together.

00:13:15.333 --> 00:13:20.320
Braden does all my archives, and he does all the videos, he's over them, he studies them.

00:13:20.320 --> 00:13:26.604
So, thank God for him, but he does that.

00:13:26.604 --> 00:13:32.693
Dina does the emails and all the other side of it, and Braden does archiving.

00:13:43.500 --> 00:13:44.200
And I thought it was interesting when I saw China going after Taiwan in the days ahead.

00:13:50.000 --> 00:13:50.800
And America—I said, 'Where is America at to defend Taiwan in this?

00:13:50.800 --> 00:13:55.600
' But they were preoccupied with something else.

00:13:57.380 --> 00:13:58.270
And I saw gray upon the soil.

00:14:08.240 --> 00:14:10.690
I saw gray; it looked like ash.

00:14:08.240 --> 00:14:13.280
It looked like something bad from Louisiana to Canada, all upon the eastern seaboard.

00:14:23.733 --> 00:14:24.516
And I said, 'What is this thick gray all over there?

00:14:24.516 --> 00:14:30.784
' And I still can't figure out what all that gray stuff is, this soot-looking stuff.

00:14:30.784 --> 00:14:35.636
It looked like thick, gooey something all over the soil, and I know it represents something.

00:14:35.636 --> 00:14:46.928
But if you go back, even with the last vision that I had with the dragon coming up three times out of the sea from Cuba—and the Lord keeps telling us, 'Watch Cuba, watch Cuba.

00:14:46.928 --> 00:14:49.648
They're being promised things.

00:14:49.648 --> 00:14:57.520
' And they showed up in Russia; they went and had the meetings there, and they even talked about it, that they sent delegates or whatever to Russia.

00:15:01.627 --> 00:15:02.800
So we see these things being talked about.

00:15:02.800 --> 00:15:08.528
So I'm trying to just paint a picture for you of all the visions that I've had, saying, 'Look.

00:15:08.528 --> 00:15:09.520
' And so here we have Cuba.

00:15:09.520 --> 00:15:12.352
He keeps saying in these paradigms, 'Watch Cuba.

00:15:12.352 --> 00:15:14.240
' And I'm like, 'Well, watch Cuba?

00:15:14.240 --> 00:15:16.133
What are we watching Cuba for?

00:15:16.133 --> 00:15:19.920
' But I saw biological things.

00:15:19.920 --> 00:15:24.792
I saw these things, I saw the dragon coming up out of the water.

00:15:24.792 --> 00:15:28.516
And it was the kind of dragon what you see in the parades.

00:15:28.516 --> 00:15:37.709
Well, China has the parades that look like those papier-mâché dragons that they're dancing, and the people are in them and they're dancing.

00:15:37.709 --> 00:15:39.520
That's the kind of dragon it was.

00:15:39.520 --> 00:15:47.880
It was like the ones that move their mouth, and it's really decorative, and they do the dances with them for their parades and stuff, their Chinese celebrations.

00:15:47.880 --> 00:15:52.080
So this is what I saw, and that was coming up and out of the water.

00:16:05.440 --> 00:16:06.768
But it was purple, a light lavender purple with a dark fin on its back, with dark purple around his eyes with white on that dark purple, and then a really bright eye that looked green.

00:16:06.768 --> 00:16:18.480
Then I saw that the feet, the claws, were dark purple as it came up out of the water, with a dark purple tail.

00:16:24.293 --> 00:16:24.996
And I think that's very interesting.

00:16:24.996 --> 00:16:30.169
I've never seen a purple dragon because usually they're red and stuff in China.

00:16:30.169 --> 00:16:34.880
So, after I saw that, then I saw China moving in and striking Taiwan.

00:16:34.880 --> 00:16:39.004
That's what it was all about after all that.

00:16:39.004 --> 00:16:43.600
So, trying to piece things together, I'm not adding to or taking away from anything.

00:16:47.280 --> 00:16:53.213
I just put the pieces together and say, 'Look, this one could fit there, and look how that all kind of goes together.

00:16:53.213 --> 00:17:07.920
' Because I believe it's the Lord talking to us to tell us to pray about these things, because He said, 'Pray for Taiwan that this does not happen,' and that megaton bomb coming over Tel Aviv and hitting Israel.

00:17:07.920 --> 00:17:14.560
But when I saw the people dancing in the streets in the days ahead, they said, 'Our deliverer has come.

00:17:14.560 --> 00:17:22.698
' The Lord said, 'I'm going to show up and show off in a way that this generation has never seen before for the Israeli people.

00:17:22.698 --> 00:17:25.280
I'm going to come through for them.

00:17:25.280 --> 00:17:31.469
' And so I just want you to be encouraged with everything I'm saying, but I believe we're about to see some radical stuff.

00:17:42.960 --> 00:17:48.560
So we pray for the enemy within America, the Red Dawn experience in the ten cities.

00:17:44.580 --> 00:17:49.440
We need to pray over that.

00:17:52.095 --> 00:17:58.000
And some of these things are going to take place, some of it's going to happen because we're in the end times and a great escalation of things will take place.

00:17:58.000 --> 00:18:00.720
Remember I said it even in the short video, 'Everything's going to change.

00:18:00.720 --> 00:18:07.280
' The Lord said it again, 'Everything you know will change within 24 hours.

00:18:07.280 --> 00:18:12.480
Life as you know it, and how you live right now, Brandon, will change within 24 hours.

00:18:12.480 --> 00:18:19.600
' A great acceleration of things is about to take place.

00:18:19.600 --> 00:18:21.733
'The wealth of the sinner is laid up for the righteous.

00:18:21.733 --> 00:18:24.400
' We're going to see that.

00:18:28.640 --> 00:18:33.120
I saw oil in the Mediterranean, I saw oil in the Gulf of Mexico, I saw oil trying to come up to back the dollar, and trying to do all this stuff as Iran is crippled in the days ahead.

00:18:33.120 --> 00:18:35.280
Now, will we see that?

00:18:45.648 --> 00:18:46.304
I pray we don't.

00:18:46.304 --> 00:18:50.240
Gas lines are going to be terrible.

00:18:50.240 --> 00:18:53.320
I saw 1970s gas shortages, miles long, where people in California couldn't get gas.

00:19:06.376 --> 00:19:07.024
And people said, 'Well, we don't buy our gas from Iran.

00:19:07.024 --> 00:19:08.320
' And I understand that, but it was about the world stage.

00:19:12.160 --> 00:19:13.560
It wasn't about America.

00:19:13.547 --> 00:19:16.320
It was about the price of the petrodollar shooting up because of a supply shortage in Iran from other nations.

00:19:16.320 --> 00:19:21.440
So I know China gets oil from there and other nations, right?

00:19:21.440 --> 00:19:23.540
So it's not just about America.

00:19:21.440 --> 00:19:28.080
It never is just about America; it's about the world.

00:19:28.080 --> 00:19:29.130
So, let's see.

00:19:32.560 --> 00:19:36.410
I pray that, like I said, I pray that doesn't happen.

00:19:34.775 --> 00:19:35.145
I pray we don't see five and six dollars a gallon, ten dollars.

00:19:35.145 --> 00:19:36.991
What was it, Braden?

00:19:37.360 --> 00:19:39.536
I saw gallons of gas go over eight dollars a gallon average.

00:19:39.536 --> 00:19:43.978
Yeah, an eight-dollar-a-gallon average is what the vision I had, and I wrote it all down.

00:19:43.978 --> 00:19:49.280
And it lasted for several months, and people were upset about it, you know, because everything went back up.

00:19:49.280 --> 00:19:57.600
So do I say every vision I have comes to pass perfectly?

00:19:57.600 --> 00:19:58.600
No.

00:19:57.600 --> 00:19:58.650
You know why?

00:19:57.600 --> 00:20:03.449
Because we have people that pray.

00:20:03.449 --> 00:20:20.018
I believe with all my heart the visions the Lord gives me are not all just prophetic, 'Thus saith the Lord,' like somebody who is a Kim Clement or whatever giving words that are prophetic.

00:20:20.018 --> 00:20:30.480
I am a watchman, and a lot of the words I give, the Lord tells me, 'You should pray.

00:20:30.480 --> 00:20:31.480
You pray.

00:20:30.480 --> 00:20:31.440
' Well, what does that tell you?

00:20:31.440 --> 00:20:39.120
Pray and change it.

00:20:39.120 --> 00:20:46.720
You're an intercessor—that's what I do, and I've done this for years.

00:20:46.720 --> 00:20:49.920
But I see these things, I see in part, hear in part.

00:20:49.920 --> 00:20:58.648
But the things I see, I believe a lot of it we can change.

00:20:58.648 --> 00:21:04.960
I believe a lot of it we can change through prayer; some of it we cannot.

00:21:04.960 --> 00:21:11.120
So it's only by intercessory prayer.

00:21:30.987 --> 00:21:31.893
So if we don't see it to pass, and you say, 'Well, that part of it didn't happen, but the war did and the escalation of it.

00:21:31.893 --> 00:21:44.480
' So, Tehran is being evacuated right now as we speak, and I think, what is that going to do?

00:21:44.480 --> 00:21:51.387
What is all this, seventeen million people all leaving at the same time?

00:21:51.387 --> 00:21:53.360
That's crazy.

00:21:53.360 --> 00:21:54.430
Can you imagine the traffic in that?

00:21:54.430 --> 00:22:08.430
When we went to Florida, and there's like how many million people in Florida, that traffic was terrible going around Miami.

00:22:08.430 --> 00:22:11.227
I was like, 'I can't imagine living here every day.

00:22:11.227 --> 00:22:17.760
' Those people were nuts, the way they drove, compared to Oklahoma.

00:22:17.760 --> 00:22:19.893
We're just backwoods people.

00:22:19.893 --> 00:22:24.160
They were just like flowing inside...

00:22:43.120 --> 00:22:44.240
I was just like, 'Oh my God.

00:22:44.240 --> 00:22:54.213
' You know, driving down the freeway, I go, "I've got to get off and get on a side road.

00:22:54.213 --> 00:22:56.400
" That's why I said, "I can't do this.

00:22:56.400 --> 00:22:57.744
" They're aggressive drivers.

00:22:57.744 --> 00:23:03.120
We're more like taking in the scenery and going real slow.

00:23:03.120 --> 00:23:08.580
Hey look, we rubberneck a lot looking at the wrecks or whatever.

00:23:08.580 --> 00:23:10.400
You've got to go.

00:23:10.400 --> 00:23:11.636
These people are like—I was like, "It's scary, isn't it?

00:23:23.600 --> 00:23:31.300
" I just can't see how they—I bet the insurance down there is nuts to have a car, you know, for your teenager.

00:23:33.936 --> 00:23:34.720
It would be like, "Yeah, it's $1,000 a month for insurance.

00:23:34.720 --> 00:23:38.640
" I'm like, "Yeah, no, we're good.

00:23:38.640 --> 00:23:47.040
" So, okay, well, let's read this prophetic word, like I said, and then we're going to pray.

00:23:47.040 --> 00:23:51.648
So this video is going to be longer today.

00:23:51.648 --> 00:24:00.987
For the people who say, "Hey, I don't want to be here," fast forward it, or what is that thing called?

00:24:00.987 --> 00:24:02.240
Double speed it.

00:24:02.240 --> 00:24:10.240
Oh, we got a microphone from somebody, so we're hoping it works better because—sorry, my voice is—I don't realize.

00:24:10.240 --> 00:24:14.272
